channel.title: Looking for a simple mac friendly PI or Delta source
channel.description:
Im running eclipse IDE and every source I have ever ran has tons and tons of errors. I have only found 1 that has worked successfully and that was only because the was a JAGGRAB integrated. I don't care about all the fancy stuff. Main points are simply stability and Working skills. The skills can be simple but I would like them to at least be there. Other than that, any mac friendly PI or Delta source will make me happy lol.
THank you
